Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:53.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.20,0:03:58.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..啊..嗯..那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,..欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子越来越麻烦了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:11.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说明大家都很需要你啦
